snippet.title: From Orbit [Official Launch Trailer]
snippet.description:
From Orbit is launching August 27, 2019
on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/668290/From_Orbit/ 
and itch.io: https://tentaclehead.itch.io/from-orbit

From Orbit is a quick and light single player Action RTS. Guide your stranded crew home as they land on alien planets, scout out the area, build defenses, harvest valuable resources, and launch back into orbit before being overwhelmed by hostile aliens.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------

Twitter: https://twitter.com/tentaclehead

Website: http://tentaclehead.com/
